---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="API Documentation - Rabiah Khanum">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 via-white to-teal-50">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
          API Documentation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Exploring the art and science of creating clear, developer-friendly API documentation
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Content Card -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 md:p-12 mb-12 border border-slate-100">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <!-- Icon or Visual Element -->
          <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-400 to-teal-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 text-center" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
            Learning Journey in Progress
          </h2>
          
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700 space-y-6">
            <p class="text-center text-lg leading-relaxed">
              I am currently deepening my expertise in API documentation, focusing on creating comprehensive, 
              developer-centric documentation that makes complex technical concepts accessible and actionable.
            </p>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-50 to-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 my-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
                What I'm Learning
              </h3>
              <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-700">
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>RESTful API documentation best practices and standards</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>OpenAPI Specification (OAS) and Swagger documentation tools</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Writing clear endpoint descriptions, request/response examples, and error handling guides</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Creating interactive API explorers and code snippets in multiple languages</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-teal-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                    <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>Authentication flows, rate limiting, and versioning documentation</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-10">
              <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
                Comprehensive samples and examples showcasing these practices will be shared here soon.
              </p>
              <div class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-teal-600 text-white rounded-lg font-medium">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
                Coming Soon
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tools & Technologies Section -->
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
          Tools & Technologies
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Swagger/OpenAPI</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">API Specification</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Postman</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">API Testing</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">ReadMe</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Documentation Hub</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-4 text-center shadow-sm">
            <div class="font-semibold text-slate-900">Redoc</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">API Docs</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
